      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle has seen some adventures and is definitely in 'fixer-upper' territory, showing significant wear and tear both inside and out. It\u2019s a great opportunity for someone handy looking for a diamond in the rough to restore or use for parts. Sold as-is, this car is ready for its next chapter with a dedicated new owner!",
      "price": 8500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
