    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine performs reliably and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience for both city commuting and longer trips. While it shows some minor signs of regular use, the interior remains clean and the mechanical components are in solid working order. This car offers a great balance of performance and value for anyone looking for a well-cared-for pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 35500.0,
